## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="4fb76-126">大文字と小文字のみが異なる名前を使用して2つの値を追加した場合、例外はスローされません。これは、推奨される方法ではありません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4fb76-126">If two values are added with names that differ only by case, no exception will be thrown, which is not a recommended practice.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4fb76-127">ただし、まったく同じ名前の2つの値を追加する<xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationException>と、がスローされます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4fb76-127">However, adding two values with the exact same name will cause the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationException> to be thrown.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4fb76-128">次に例を示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4fb76-128">For example:</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
void ISerializable.GetObject(SerializationInfo info, StreamingContext context)  
{  
   // This will not cause an exception to be thrown.  
   info.AddValue("ABC", true);  
   info.AddValue("abc", false);  
   // However, this will cause the SerializationException to be thrown.  
   info.AddValue("XYZ", true);  
   info.AddValue("XYZ", false);  
}  
```  
  
```vb  
Private Sub GetObjectData(ByVal info As SerializationInfo, _  
ByVal context As StreamingContext)  
   ' This will not cause an exception to be thrown.  
   info.AddValue("ABC", "upper case")  
   info.AddValue("abc", "lower case")  
   ' However, this will cause the SerializationException to be thrown.  
   info.AddValue("XYZ", "same case")  
   info.AddValue("XYZ", "same case")  
End Sub  
```
